1}=3Db}"></span>.
</p><p>The exponent is usually shown as a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.o=
rg/wiki/Superscript" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Superscript">superscrip=
t</a> to the right of the base as <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>b</i><sup><i>n=
</i></sup></span> or in computer code as <code>b^n</code>. This <a href=3D"=
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Binary_operation" title=3D"Binary operation">=
binary operation</a> is often read as "<span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=
=3D"font-style:italic;">b</span> to the power <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" =
style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</span>"; it may also be referred to as "<spa=
n class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">b</span> raised to th=
e <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</span>th powe=
r", "the <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</span>=
th power of <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">b</sp=
an>",<sup id=3D"cite_ref-2" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
edia.org/wiki/Exponentiation#cite_note-2"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</s=
pan>2<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> or, most briefly, "<sp=
an class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">b</span> to the <spa=
n class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</span>".
</p><p>The above definition of <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-ele=
ment-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" st=
yle=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" a=
lttext=3D"{\displaystyle b^{n}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <msup>
          <mi>b</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>n</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle b^{n}}</annot=
ation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/b8f8f52cd26bb201e02c8d1b3619a3a682f44dbc" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
