-align: -0.338ex; width:2.216ex; height:2.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle b^{=
n}}"></span> immediately implies several properties, in particular the mult=
iplication rule:<sup id=3D"cite_ref-3" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https=
