<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Zero_exponent">Zero exponen=
t</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket"=
>[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DExponentia=
tion&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D7" title=3D"Edit section: Zero exponen=
t"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></sp=
an></div>
<p>As mentioned earlier, a (nonzero) number raised to the <span class=3D"te=
xhtml">0</span> power is <span class=3D"texhtml">1</span>:<sup id=3D"cite_r=
ef-26" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponen=
tiation#cite_note-26"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>25<span class=3D=
"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-:1_1-2" class=3D"refer=
ence"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponentiation#cite_note-:1-=
1"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>1<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</sp=
an></a></sup>
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e b^{0}=3D1.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <msup>
          <mi>b</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mn>0</mn>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>1.</mn>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle b^{0}=3D1.}</=
annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/de10f50a06d8e714f55212cadf1da761bcec4c1a" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:6.96ex; height:2.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle b^{0=
}=3D1.}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>This value is also obtained by the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/Empty_product" title=3D"Empty product">empty product</a> convention, wh=
ich may be used in every <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algebraic=
_structure" title=3D"Algebraic structure">algebraic structure</a> with a mu=
ltiplication that has an <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiplic=
ative_identity" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Multiplicative identity">ide=
ntity</a>. This way the formula
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e b^{m+n}=3Db^{m}\cdot b^{n}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <msup>
          <mi>b</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>m</mi>
            <mo>+</mo>
            <mi>n</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <msup>
          <mi>b</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>m</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>=E2=8B=85<!-- =E2=8B=85 --></mo>
        <msup>
          <mi>b</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>n</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle b^{m+n}=3Db^{=
m}\cdot b^{n}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/259b25c515e091594d2f0ea2b75bf2628ce45f51" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:14.604ex; height:2.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle b^=
{m+n}=3Db^{m}\cdot b^{n}}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>also holds for <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline">=
<span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"displa=
y: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle n=3D0}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>n</mi>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>0</mn>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle n=3D0}</annot=
ation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/26819344e55f5e671c76c07c18eb4291fcec85ae" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:5.656ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle n=
=3D0}"></span>.
</p><p>The case of <span class=3D"texhtml">0<sup>0</sup></span> is controve=
rsial. In contexts where only integer powers are considered, the value <spa=
n class=3D"texhtml">1</span> is generally assigned to <span class=3D"texhtm=
l">0<sup>0</sup></span> but, otherwise, the choice of whether to assign it =
a value and what value to assign may depend on context. <link rel=3D"mw-ded=
uplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1320445320"><span r=
ole=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable crossreference">For=
 more details, see <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zero_to_the_pow=
er_of_zero" title=3D"Zero to the power of zero">Zero to the power of zero</=
a>.</span>
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Negative_exponents">Negativ=
e exponents</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsectio=
n-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3D=
Exponentiation&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D8" title=3D"Edit section: Ne=
gative exponents"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracke=
t">]</span></span></div>
<p>Exponentiation with negative exponents is defined by the following ident=
ity, which holds for any integer <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font=
-style:italic;">n</span> and nonzero <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"=
font-style:italic;">b</span>:<sup id=3D"cite_ref-:1_1-3" class=3D"reference=
"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponentiation#cite_note-:1-1"><=
span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>1<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span><=
/a></sup>
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e b^{-n}=3D{\frac {1}{b^{n}}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <msup>
          <mi>b</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
            <mi>n</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mn>1</mn>
            <msup>
              <mi>b</mi>
              <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <mi>n</mi>
              </mrow>
            </msup>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle b^{-n}=3D{\fr=
ac {1}{b^{n}}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/3bb09df7fe703ced09c5c135a5cb86c6e94ea77b" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -2.005ex; width:9.645ex; height:5.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle b^{=
-n}=3D{\frac {1}{b^{n}}}}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>Raising 0 to a negative exponent is undefined but, in some circumstances=
, it may be interpreted as infinity (<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-ma=
th-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a1=
1y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/Mat=
hML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \infty }">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi mathvariant=3D"normal">=E2=88=9E<!-- =E2=88=9E --></mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \infty }</ann=
otation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
