Since a negative number times another negative is positive, we have:</p><bl=
ockquote><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span =
class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: non=
