</p><p>If <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">x</span=
> is a positive real number, and <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-e=
lement-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" =
