-align: -0.671ex; width:11.96ex; height:3.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle b^{=
z}=3De^{(z\ln b)},}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>where <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span cla=
