<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id=3D"Failure_of_power_and_logari=
thm_identities">Failure of power and logarithm identities</h4><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=
