>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div=
>
<p>A <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiplicative_group" title=
=3D"Multiplicative group">multiplicative group</a> is a set with as <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Associative_operation" class=3D"mw-redire=
ct" title=3D"Associative operation">associative operation</a> denoted as mu=
ltiplication, that has an <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Identity=
_element" title=3D"Identity element">identity element</a>, and such that ev=
ery element has an inverse.
</p><p>So, if <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">G</=
span> is a group, <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline">=
<span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"displa=
y: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle x^{n}}">
