t state <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>Ax</i></span> of the system.<sup id=3D"c=
ite_ref-43" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ex=
ponentiation#cite_note-43"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>41<span cla=
ss=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> This is the standard interpretation =
of a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markov_chain" title=3D"Markov=
