<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"In_programming_languages">I=
n programming languages</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"m=
w-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.=
